---
title: Ginger & Hoisin-Glazed Chicken with Pear Slaw & Sesame Fries
description: Sweet and salty hoisin sauce to drizzle over golden chicken is a great combination. Try serving with sesame fries and you’ve got another match. Putting sweet pear in a creamy slaw and adding it to the ensemble is yet one more amazing flavour combo. Altogether that's one stellar dish that everyone is going to be raving about.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca534bc2f2c4b379aae6be-90634028.jpeg
